<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=371&amp;p=388#p388"><![CDATA[
3/14(Sat.)My journey to thank all the people responsible for my morning coffee /<br />Board game time! The werewolves of millers hollow.(Host:Nora)<br /><br /><br />session 1.<br />My journey to thank all the people responsible for my morning coffee <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.ted.com/talks/a_j_jacobs_my_journey_to_thank_all_the_people_responsible_for_my_morning_coffee?utm_campaign=tedspread&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=tedcomshare">https://www.ted.com/talks/a_j_jacobs_my ... edcomshare</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />1. Do you have the same problem of focusing on the negative? If you do, what do you usually do to release your depression?<br />2. Has a stranger showed his/her appreciation for you? What is that situation? How do you feel?<br />3. Are you grateful to someone you don't know his/her name for all that he/she has done? <br />4. What if you are going to thank someone or something, who or what will you start? <br />5. Let's start our journey to thank people who makes a contribution to your life! Turn to the people beside you and say &quot;thank you&quot; to them.<br /><br />session 2.<br />Board game time! The werewolves of millers hollow<br /><br />We are  going to gave a special session- classic board game: the werewolves of millers hollow! The game is based on the Russian game Mafia, and suitable for beginners. you can also learn how to become a great debater. Come here to join us with pleasant mood.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25764">Michelle Hsu</a> — Fri Mar 13, 2020 12:46 am</p><hr />
